Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 11th century,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the invasion by Denmark's army \Nand the Vikings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,continued to intensify.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ENGLAND 1012 AD
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In October,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the attacks, which had continued for several years,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,reached a turning point.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,VICINITY OF JELLING DENMARK \NKING SWEYN'S ESTATE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me \Nto withdraw my troops from England?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not withdrawing. We're letting them rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Marching in the winter weakens them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the soldiers rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to strike next summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, shall lead an army in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, suddenly we get a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,ENGLAND COAST \NDANISH ARMY BASE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need those pirates for now, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd be able to earn a lot this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything, \Nnow that the army is staying put.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate being a hired hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Askeladd going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a shame to spend all winter like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And we already raided all the good villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to do what the birds do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to where the food is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,KINGDOM OF FRANCE \NVICINITY OF LOIRE RIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a ram.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the crossbowmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One. Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alternate fire with two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. Retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the Franks are fighting \Namongst themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The fort's defended by only a few men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The attackers have 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they attacked the fort head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the local clan's headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Doesn't it smell like treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what you're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll side with the attackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's smash open the treasure chest, \Nand take everything inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering why we came to the boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your predictions were spot-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make up our loss from England.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,NORMANNI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Make contact with their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him this message:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're terrible at battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, my men will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a once-in-a-lifetime offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall lead you to victory, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the fort falls, we will take half of the spoils.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall attack again tomorrow morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,After you deliver the message, stay in their camp, \Nand observe the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Then go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how many people I've killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I went scouting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I also brought up the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've accomplished enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you close the deal, I'll give you three gold pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear in the name of Tyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't test me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you plan to keep running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to bring me at least one head with a helmet, \Nif you want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's okay \Nto let him handle the negotiation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers are short-tempered \Nwhen they're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They might kill the messenger, \Nbefore the negotiations start. It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if we lose some kid that follows us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no place for a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone who can speak Norse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you? What language is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a spy from the fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Secure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone who can speak Norse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You want half of the spoils?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You mercenaries. Don't push your luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"You want half of the spoils? \NDon't push your luck."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty confident in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Normanni kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Normanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people from the north attacking England?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Those people from the north attacking England?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a kid can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep attacking the front gate, \Nyour men are just going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Their defenses are weak on the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to attack there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plan is ill-considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The river that leads to the lake gets steeper upstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's even a waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ship sunk downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what would happen \Nif you attacked from the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"That's what would happen \Nif you attacked from the lake."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you want to turn down my offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Askeladd and his hundred men are going \Nto join the defenders in the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll do the same thing if I die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't signal that the deal has been closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to make enemies \Nof a hundred fierce men from the Northern Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're lying, I'm going to cut off your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're telling the truth, \Nthen in the name of Jesus Christ,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll share my bread equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll share my bread equally."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a memento from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Thorfinn's signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,One high arrow, and two low arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cross the pass before the moon rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're stuck guarding the ship the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to fight too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that fat general.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You said, the dragon climbed the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Last night, \Nthe soldiers guarding the ship all reported they saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bad omen, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends haven't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to see it too."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"The sun is already up."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just attack, you fat-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You said something mean just now, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like our entertainment for tonight is going \Nto be cutting off your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward march.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward march.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're late. Bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your heart into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The battlefield is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the same every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a bridge on the west side too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how many men we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Which one is their leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The one with the feather on his helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A head with a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He was lying. Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You let the kid escape. \NYou haven't captured the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking you'll go home, \Nonce the snow falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going home until the fort is captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Row. Full speed ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever gets there first gets twice as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your heart into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were friendly forces. \NAll troops, forward. Don't stop until the fort falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Never imagined they'd carry their ship over the pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighty men from the right wing, \Ngo to the boat landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Crossbowmen, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The lake's not a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shallow pond that makes for a perfect attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They pierced my shield, \Neven though they're so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They got Olov.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Crossbowmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a few losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire as much as you can before they land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They stopped attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they ran out of arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Men. Prepare to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, no. \N-Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is for the captain. \N-Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-That kid's crazy. \N-Get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go. Storm them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Go on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding the gate's too hard for these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, and kill them all, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One. Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Normannis are crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That fortress was no match \Nagainst my military tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain of the fortress defense died in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers said, a kid did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Never underestimate a Normanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I send him back now, \Nhe's going to become an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys came over the pass, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll probably go back the same way, \Ncarrying the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when we'll attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A sailor on land is like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message for General Jabbathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The treasure room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They also plundered the church \Nand the houses of all the leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They took everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message for the leader of the Franks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As for your half of the spoils,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you get victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and we get the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fine with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're being quite generous here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We let you have the fort, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-You bastards. \N-Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-They'll descend the waterfall. \N-Savages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get the boats. \N-You pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-All boats in the fort have been destroyed. \N-You greedy beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You scammers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You country bumpkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand French.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, shall we call it a night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn hasn't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. I bet he's dead anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there's more treasure for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tough, kid. Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the captain's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, did you cut it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I, warrior from Iceland, son of Thors, Thorfinn,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of my father's sword, \Nchallenge you, Askeladd, to a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To avenge my father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey. \N-He wants to duel now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I, son of Olaf, Askeladd,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of Artorius, my ancestor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,accept your challenge, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,ask me again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Row, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry up, they'll capture the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard. Don't play the fool with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if there's a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Franks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go home. \N-We struck it big.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll survive the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:24.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,11世紀。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:28.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デンマーク軍およびヴァイキングによる侵攻は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.27,0:00:30.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,激化の一途をたどっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:36.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ENGLAND 1012 AD
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そして10月。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:49.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,数年間にわたって継続された攻撃は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:51.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,転換点を迎える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:58.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ではイングランドから兵を退かれると？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:02.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,退くのではない。休めるのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,冬の行軍は兵力を浪費する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:12.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,派兵した軍にも英気を養わせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:15.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,は。仰せのとおりに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:17.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,夏だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:23.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来年の夏には大攻勢をかける。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,余も兵を率いて陣頭に立つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いきなり休みかぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:37.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,郷に帰りてぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,海賊連中も当分用なしだな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:47.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,…今年も稼げると思ったのによー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:50.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,正規の兵が動かねぇんじゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:54.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これだから雇われ仕事はなぁ～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:59.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうするつもりだぁ？アシェラッドは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:06.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このまま冬を越すのはちと寂しくねーか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,めぼしい村は平らげちまったしよぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だよなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:14.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうするつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どーするもこーするも…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,渡り鳥と一緒さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,餌のある所に移動するだけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,グズグズするなぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラムだぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:52.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,弩兵集まれぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せーのぉっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二隊交互で斉射だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かまえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:02.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だめだ！退けぇーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フランク人同士の小競り合いか…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,砦側は少数。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,攻め手は800ってとこか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの砦に正面からぶつかるとはなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,土豪の本拠地ってとこか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:51.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうだ？お宝の匂いがプンプンしねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これが狙いってわけか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やるか。アシェラッド
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,攻め手につくぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:04.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,宝箱をブッ壊して中身をゴッソリいただこう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よっしゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こぉんなド田舎でどうするつもりかと思ったけど、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さすがアシェラッドだぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:13.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱ首領の読みは間違いねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イングランドで稼げなかった分、取り戻すぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんじゃトルフィン！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へっ。出番だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,参戦だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,参戦だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,攻め手の親分にわたりをつけといで。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,口上はこうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴殿の戦はァヘタだっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見るに堪えん。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よって我が兵団お助け申す。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,千載一遇わたりに船。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:38.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,必ずや汝らを勝利へ導くであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:43.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,砦が陥ちた暁には戦利品の半分を所望する。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,明朝再び突撃されよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:50.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,伝えたら奴らの兵営に残って状況を見張れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかったら行け
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:58.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行けよトルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これまでにどれだけ殺したと思ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,斥候にも出たし、
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しんがりも務めた。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手柄は十分に立てた。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なのに…てめぇは…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよ。ほうびが欲しいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,交渉成立なら金貨3枚くれてやるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:32.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ティール神に誓ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ざけんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつまで逃げ回ってるつもりだ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウホホッこわい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,からかっただけだって。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だがなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:51.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それならカブト首の1つくらい、\Nとってこなきゃあならんだろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,相変わらずだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:05.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもいいのか？大事な交渉任せちまって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,劣勢の兵は気が立ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:11.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,交渉の前に殺されるなんざよくある話さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,拾ったガキなら惜しくはないだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんじゃア！わっぱ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ガキの来る所じゃねぇぞ、コラァ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,軍使だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ノルド語を話せる奴はいるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだこのガキ？何語だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フランク人じゃねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,砦の奴らのスパイか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま、捕らえとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレは軍使だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ノルド語を話せる奴はいるか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:00.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦利品の半分をよこせだとォ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:04.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,傭兵風情が図に乗りおって！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たいした自信だな、ええ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ノルマンニの小僧よ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ノルマンニ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:17.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イングランドを荒らし回っている北の民か
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,小僧でもわかる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,正門ばかり攻めても兵が死ぬだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,湖の防備は薄い。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:31.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレたちはそこを叩く
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,浅知恵だな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:36.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,湖に至る川は上るにつれ勾配がきつくなる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あまつさえ滝もあるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我々の船も下流で往生しておる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,湖から攻撃せぬのはそういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:51.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,断るか？この話。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:56.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならばアシェラッドの兵100人は砦側と手を結ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレが死んだ場合も同じだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,商談成立の合図がない場合、
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:05.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,北海の猛者100人がお前の敵になる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よかろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,閣下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:14.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:18.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様の言葉が偽りであればその首を斬り落とす！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まことであればイエス・キリストの名において
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,パンを等しく分かち合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレの短剣を返してくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親父の形見なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィンからの知らせだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,高く1本。低く2本…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:56.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,急ぐぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,月が昇りきる前に峠を越えるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:04.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ずっと船の護衛かよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレも戦いてえなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クソッ。あのデブ将軍め！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:13.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あそこか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:23.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,竜だぁぁぁーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,山の上だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,竜が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,竜が山をのぼったじゃと？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:46.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい。昨夜、船の守備兵全員が見たとの報告が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほぉ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,凶兆です閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワシも一度見てみたいもんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,小僧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様の仲間来ぬではないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう陽が昇ってしまったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいから突撃しろデブ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すぐにわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:13.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今なんか悪口言っただろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:17.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうやら貴様の首は今宵の余興になりそうだな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,前進用意！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,前進用意！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,前進ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,突撃ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いかん。始まっちまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:54.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,出遅れたぞ！野郎ども！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気合いを入れろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦場が待ってるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何度来ても同じだぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああんもうっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,西側にもハシゴをかけろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,犠牲を厭うな！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい。敵の大将はどいつだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,羽飾りのついたカブトが見えるだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アイツだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カブト首
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様ッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:34.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やはりウソか！コロセーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,小僧を殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お～の～れぇぇぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,小僧は逃がすわ砦は陥ちぬわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:49.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうなってるんじゃこの軍はーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,雪が降れば帰れると思うとんじゃろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうはいかんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,砦が陥ちるまでは絶対に…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よっこらぁせーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,漕げェ！全速力ゥ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一番乗りは倍の分け前だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:15.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気合い入れろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:23.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは友軍じゃ！全軍進めーっ！\N砦を陥とすのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,担いで峠越えをするとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うろたえるなっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,右翼の80人は船着き場へ行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,弩隊、来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お粗末だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,湖側は防壁どころか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:54.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,絶好の浅瀬なんだもんよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いよぉし！ブッ込むぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:08.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだァ！？この距離で盾を貫きやがった！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウーロフが殺られたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,弩か。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多少損害が出るな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今なら格好の的だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,上陸される前にできるだけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:30.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子供…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,攻撃がやんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,矢が切れたのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:46.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,上陸用意だ野郎ども！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,チャンスだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しまった！\N殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,隊長の仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:34.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たたっ斬れ！\N逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いけぇ！なだれ込め！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よぉし！暴れまくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,門の方は大丈夫なのかね？コイツら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちゃちゃっと殺れよー野郎ども
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せェェのぉおっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:44.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんて奴らだ…ノルマンニ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:57.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワシの用兵術にかかってはこんな砦イチコロよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,砦の守備隊長は戦死しました。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:05.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敗兵の話によると子供の仕業とか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの小僧か！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:09.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,侮れんなノルマンニ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:13.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このまま帰しては我らの敵となるやも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いかがいたしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,連中は峠を越えてきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,帰りも船を担いでいくだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこを叩く。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:27.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸に上がった船乗りなど赤子同然よ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,閣下ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ジャバザ将軍に！ご報告ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ？申せ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:41.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほっ、宝物庫が！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワシの宝…は？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,有力者の家や教会も荒らされております！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,金目のものは何もかも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なっ…だっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、そっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フランク人の長に申し上げーーる！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:05.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦利品の半分として、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴殿は勝利を。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我らは財宝を！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:20.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,文句あるまいな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:23.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これでも謙虚な方だと思うぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,砦はくれてやるんだからなァ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:31.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おにょれぇぇぇ！\Nいかん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴ら滝を下る気だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,船を出せ！それが…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:38.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,砦にあった船は全て壊されてしまいまして
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,サギ師～！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,田舎モ～ン！\Nあ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フランク語はわからんな～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:48.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さてと。おいとまするか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィンがまだだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あらホント。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ、どーせ死んでる死んでる。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:56.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,分け前増えてよかったじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きてたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しぶといガキだな\Nケガはねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:11.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:13.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大将首だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:16.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へぇ。とったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,約束だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:24.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イヤとは言わせねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アイスランドの戦士、トールズの子トルフィン。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:35.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が父の剣にかけてアシェラッドに決闘を申し込む。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴君は我が父の仇であるがゆえに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいおいこんな時もかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくやるなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウォラフの子アシェラッド。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が祖アルトリウスの名にかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィンの挑戦を受けよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:54.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,…が、
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,後にしてくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今はこっから逃げるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,漕げ！野郎ども！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:06.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,グズグズしてると川を押さえられるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！てめぇ！ふざけんなーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:16.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,竜がなんだっつーんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:17.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怖かねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:18.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,んだんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:19.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,んでもヨォ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:41.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さらばだーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:44.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フランクの衆よーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:49.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,家～っ！\N大儲けだーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:51.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,冬が越せるーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:56.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,っしゃあ！
